info:
  title: E-Commerce Platform API
  version: 1.0.0
  description: Production-ready REST API for managing users, products, and orders
  contact:
    email: api-support@example.com

servers:
  - url: https://api.example.com/v1
    description: Production server

security:
  - bearerAuth: []

components:
  securitySchemes:
    bearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: JWT

  schemas:
    User:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - email
        - name
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
          example: "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000"
        email:
          type: string
          format: email
          example: "john.doe@example.com"
        name:
          type: string
          example: "John Doe"
        shippingAddress:
          type: string
          example: "123 Main St, New York, NY 10001"

    Product:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - name
        - description
        - price
        - category
        - stockCount
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
          example: "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001"
        name:
          type: string
          example: "Wireless Headphones"
        description:
          type: string
          example: "High-quality wireless headphones with noise cancellation"
        price:
          type: number
          format: decimal
          example: 99.99
        category:
          type: string
          example: "electronics"
        stockCount:
          type: integer
          example: 50

    OrderItem:
      type: object
      required:
        - productId
        - quantity
        - unitPrice
      properties:
        productId:
          type: string
          format: uuid
          example: "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001"
        quantity:
          type: integer
          example: 2
        unitPrice:
          type: number
          format: decimal
          example: 99.99

    OrderStatus:
      type: string
      enum:
        - pending
        - confirmed
        - shipped
        - delivered
        - cancelled
      example: "confirmed"

    Order:
      type: object
      required:
        - id
        - userId
        - items
        - total
        - status
        - createdAt
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
          example: "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174002"
        userId:
          type: string
          format: uuid
          example: "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000"
        items:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/OrderItem'
          example:
            - productId: "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174001"
              quantity: 2
              unitPrice: 99.99
        total:
          type: number
          format: decimal
          example: 199.98
        status:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/OrderStatus'
        createdAt:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          example: "2024-01-15T10:30:00Z"

    ProblemDetail:
      type: object
      required:
        - type
        - title
        - status
        - detail
      properties:
        type:
          type: string
          format: uri
          example: "https://api.example.com/errors/validation-error"
        title:
          type: string
          example: "Validation Error"
        status:
          type: integer
          example: 400
        detail:
          type: string
          example: "The request payload is invalid"

    PaginatedUsers:
      type: object
      required:
        - data
        - nextCursor
        - hasMore
      properties:
        data:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/User'
        nextCursor:
          type: string
          example: "eyJpZCI6IjEyM2U0NTY3LWU4OWItMTJkMy1hNDU2LTQyNjYxNDE3NDAwMCJ9"
        hasMore:
          type: boolean
          example: true

    PaginatedProducts:
      type: object
      required:
        - data
        - nextCursor
        - hasMore
      properties:
        data:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Product'
        nextCursor:
          type: string
          example: "eyJpZCI6IjEyM2U0NTY3LWU4OWItMTJkMy1hNDU2LTQyNjYxNDE3NDAwMSJ9"
        hasMore:
          type: boolean
          example: true

    PaginatedOrders:
      type: object
      required:
        - data
        - nextCursor
        - hasMore
      properties:
        data:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Order'
        nextCursor:
          type: string
          example: "eyJpZCI6IjEyM2U0NTY3LWU4OWItMTJkMy1hNDU2LTQyNjYxNDE3NDAwMiJ9"
        hasMore:
          type: boolean
          example: true
